**Description:** **: This module is a collection of utility functions designed for processing text and image files using the X.AI API. It handles tasks such as initializing an API client, reading and analyzing text files, encoding and resizing images, cleaning filenames, and generating structured outputs like descriptions, document types, and suggested filenames. The purpose is to simplify interactions with X.AI APIs for cleanup tasks, including error handling and logging for robustness.

